ultanas, ground allspice, ground cinnamon, ground nutmeg, egg, reserved sago and milk and reserved brown sugar-breadcrumb mixture and mix <b>10 sec\/speed 5<b>."},{"content":"Transfer into prepared pudding basin, cover with a sheet of baking paper and secure lid. Place pudding basin into Varoma dish. Rinse and dry mixing bowl."},{"content":"Place water into mixing bowl. Place Varoma into position and steam <b>60 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Check water level in mixing bowl and top up if necessary. Place Varoma back into position and steam for a further <b>60 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Check water level in mixing bowl again and top up if necessary. Place Varoma back into position and steam for a further <b>60 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Check water level in mixing bowl again and top up if necessary. Place Varoma back into position and steam for a final <b>60 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b> or until pudding is cooked through and consistent in colour. Your pudding is cooked through when a wooden skewer inserted into the centre of the pudding comes out clean. Serve warm."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Serve pudding warm with <em>Brandy cream sauce<\/em> or <em>Brandy cashew cream, <\/em>garnished with fresh cherries.<em><br><\/em>","If using a different size pudding basin or baking tin please be aware cooking times will be lengthened or shortened accordingly. Continue checking water level and topping up as necessary."],"basicInfo":["medium","15m","14h 45m","8 portions"]}